  <item>
      <name>Fernian Ash Rod</name>
    <detail>Wondrous item, Spellcasting Focus</detail>
    <type>G</type>
    <magic>1</magic>
    <weight>2</weight>
    <property></property>
    <text>An arcane focus is a special item designed to channel the power of arcane spells. A sorcerer, warlock, or wizard can use such an item as a spellcasting focus.
An imbued wood focus is a rod, staff, or wand cut from a tree infused with extraplanar energy. If you're a spellcaster, you can use this item as a spellcasting focus.
When you cast a damage-dealing spell using this item as your spellcasting focus, you gain a +1 bonus to one fire damage roll of the spell.
Source: Eberron: Rising from the Last War p. 277, Wayfinder's Guide to Eberron p. 114</text>
    </item>
